{"tid":189191,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰業績虧損高層竟加薪　CEO年薪1050萬","createTime":"2017-04-06T09:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T13:04:20.000Z","uid":57460,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b49dd2becd7c1edfbccf86b973a06b59ceca321","tid":189191,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"國泰業績虧損高層竟加薪　CEO年薪1050萬<br />\n04月05日(三) 22:40   <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170405/bkn-20170405224011937-0405_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170405%2Fbkn-20170405224011937-0405_00822_001.html&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=1cb08ae0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170405/bkn-20170405224011937-0405_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n朱國樑薪酬達1050.7萬港元，按年增加超過4%。(資料圖片)<br />\n國泰航空去年業績盈轉虧，為2008年金融海嘯後首次錄得虧損，管理層早前宣布未來3年削減30%管理人手成本以「填氹」。不過，包括行政總裁朱國樑在內多名高級管理層，去年薪酬不減反增，當中朱國樑薪酬達1050.7萬港元，按年增加超過4%。 <br />\n<br />\n國泰最新年報資料顯示，2016年主席史樂山薪酬為84.5萬港元，較2015年顯著減少逾57%。不過，其餘多名高級管理層薪酬不減反增，除朱國樑之外，董事和常務總裁何杲去年薪酬達1201.4萬港元，按年增加逾8%；財務董事馬天偉去年薪酬較2015年更顯著增加超過10%，金額達1073.2萬港元。 <br />\n<br />\n因管理不善而在全球最佳航空公司排名節節下跌的國泰航空，去年業績盈轉虧，全年虧損5.75億港元，主因是去年燃油對沖虧損高達84.5億港元，僅輕微少於2015年度的84.7億港元虧損，連續3年累計對沖虧損高逾178億港元。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">管理不善都有人工加，<br />\n但經理級以上就冇！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e50493d738270f58b4f39421c834959560b14eb2","tid":189191,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7dca16fd93906b6efec93f13be0076005a2b8ee","tid":189191,"uid":51389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"係D港豬仲成日都要搭因航，好似全地球得佢一間航空公司咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cc376e2d95c9489f34d0c3cb098246e3276896","tid":189191,"uid":25213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係D港豬仲成日都要搭因航，好似全地球得佢一間航空公司咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搭乜先唔係港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f18cb07faefdabec0e9dc5fec87dd4fa6398ce3","tid":189191,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"用萬里通搭有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29f7bebdb93147cc93af3ca3b5b092417b18fd3","tid":189191,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"肥上瘦下是常識吧"},{"pid":"8f13dba3907ea3ccac926d26795fa65a4d05adc2","tid":189191,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:22:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a270989030c242d45081bebe131a0664e7bd6750","tid":189191,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"一年人工都唔夠買北角400呎單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6777a902c2dff9ddc5017a687f58ab7106b406d","tid":189191,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a5be506b12d78960097ccd3981d5b3d2bbb5ac2","tid":189191,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一年人工都唔夠買北角400呎單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高層喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要CEO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 